"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-04-03-Two-world-champions-one-Olympic-spot-Li-ousts-Shen-in-cruel-battle-1suHEIEQqju-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"CGTN  Copied  China's Li Fabin reacts after the men's 67 kg event at the IWF World Cup in Phuket, Thailand, April 2, 2024.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 327, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 219, \"end\": 224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.809236077935269, \"rank\": 0.23573333697954077, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 227, \"end\": 229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.820197953480685e-13, \"text\": \"Li\", \"types\": [\"Q11173\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\"}, {\"begin\": 295, \"end\": 301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phuket_province\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.1581770529944364e-13, \"text\": \"Phuket\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phuket_province\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phuket_province\"}, {\"begin\": 303, \"end\": 311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9971135437408711, \"rank\": 0.00289447846956287, \"text\": \"Thailand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP  When the International Weightlifting Federation (IWF)'s General Council and the International Olympic Committee approved reshuffling the weightlifting classes for the 2024 Paris Olympics, Shen Lijun found himself caught between a rock and a hard place.\", \"from\": 328, \"to\": 586, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 343, \"end\": 381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Weightlifting_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Weightlifting Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Weightlifting_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Weightlifting_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 390, \"end\": 405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_Council_of_the_Trades_Union_Congress\", \"score\": 0.9999981719423314, \"rank\": 1.8153246252150522e-06, \"text\": \"General Council\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_Council_of_the_Trades_Union_Congress\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/General_Council_of_the_Trades_Union_Congress\"}, {\"begin\": 414, \"end\": 445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The weight category in which he had won the gold medal in the Tokyo Olympics, the men's 67kg, was among those that got the axe.\", \"from\": 588, \"to\": 715, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Suddenly, the 31-year-old veteran had to face a daunting decision: bulk up to compete in the 73kg category, slim down to the 61kg category or forfeit the chance to represent China in Paris altogether.\", \"from\": 716, \"to\": 916, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 890, \"end\": 895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.809236077935269, \"rank\": 0.23573333697954077, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 899, \"end\": 904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.9824778853047873e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After careful contemplation, he made the bold choice to embark on an extreme weight-cutting journey, determined to transition to the 61kg division.\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"China's Shen Lijun during the men's 61 kg final at the IWF World Cup in Phuket, Thailand, April 2, 2024.\", \"from\": 1067, \"to\": 1171, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1067, \"end\": 1072, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.809236077935269, \"rank\": 0.23573333697954077, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1139, \"end\": 1145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phuket_province\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.1581770529944364e-13, \"text\": \"Phuket\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phuket_province\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phuket_province\"}, {\"begin\": 1147, \"end\": 1155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9971135437408711, \"rank\": 0.00289447846956287, \"text\": \"Thailand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP  This decision presented Shen with yet another predicament.\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1236, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite China's undisputed dominance in weightlifting,they faced a restriction of sending only one athlete per weight class to the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1383, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1245, \"end\": 1250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.809236077935269, \"rank\": 0.23573333697954077, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This meant that Shen had to go head-to-head with his fellow countryman Li Fabin, the reigning Olympic champion in the 67kg category, for a single Olympic spot.\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1543, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1455, \"end\": 1457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.820197953480685e-13, \"text\": \"Li\", \"types\": [\"Q11173\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having opted not to compete in the 67kg event in the previous four qualifying tournaments in order to protect his body from excessive strain, the 2024 IWF World Cup emerged as Shen's last opportunity to outperform Li and claim the coveted spot in Paris.\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1798, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1759, \"end\": 1761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.820197953480685e-13, \"text\": \"Li\", \"types\": [\"Q11173\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\"}, {\"begin\": 1792, \"end\": 1797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.9824778853047873e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shen was well aware of the intimidating task ahead of him.\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1857, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In his quest to maximize weight loss, Shen resorted to a rigorous regimen that included minimal food intake in the days leading up to the competition, relying only on essential nutrients for sustenance.\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 2061, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"China's Shen Lijun celebrates after winning the gold medal in the men's 67 kg weightlifting event at the Olympics in Tokyo, Japan, July 25, 2021.\", \"from\": 2063, \"to\": 2208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2063, \"end\": 2068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.809236077935269, \"rank\": 0.23573333697954077, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 2180, \"end\": 2185, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9997043228785116, \"rank\": 0.00029576457202208433, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 2187, \"end\": 2192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9683478533192695, \"rank\": 0.01803919070858807, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP  However, transitioning to a new weight category amidst a field of elite competitors in the World Cup proved to be a formidable challenge.\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2352, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite giving his all, Shen encountered a series of setbacks during the men's 61 kg final on Tuesday, failing to secure any of his three snatch attempts.\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2507, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ultimately, he made the tough decision to withdraw from the tournament.\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2579, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a striking contrast, Li showcased an exceptional performance, surpassing his own snatch world record and emerging victorious in the total category with 146-166-312.\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2748, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2605, \"end\": 2607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.820197953480685e-13, \"text\": \"Li\", \"types\": [\"Q11173\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it was Hampton Morris who stole the spotlight as the unexpected dark horse, stunning the crowd with a monumental final lift that not only shattered Li's clean and jerk world record but also made him the first American man in 55 years to achieve a senior-level world record.\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 3026, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2760, \"end\": 2767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Hampton\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0866333289611676e-16, \"text\": \"Hampton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Hampton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Hampton\"}, {\"begin\": 2768, \"end\": 2774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benny_Morris\", \"score\": 0.9053133508858353, \"rank\": 0.10458991232378091, \"text\": \"Morris\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benny_Morris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benny_Morris\"}, {\"begin\": 2901, \"end\": 2903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.820197953480685e-13, \"text\": \"Li\", \"types\": [\"Q11173\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By the end of it all, despite Li's achievement of earning two gold medals in snatch and on total, guaranteeing his place in Paris, a profound sense of heaviness and mixed emotions enveloped him.\", \"from\": 3028, \"to\": 3222, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3058, \"end\": 3060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.820197953480685e-13, \"text\": \"Li\", \"types\": [\"Q11173\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\"}, {\"begin\": 3152, \"end\": 3157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.9824778853047873e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"China's Li Fabin during the medal ceremony of the men's 67 kg weightlifting event at the IWF World Cup in Phuket, Thailand, April 2, 2024.\", \"from\": 3224, \"to\": 3362, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3224, \"end\": 3229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.809236077935269, \"rank\": 0.23573333697954077, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 3232, \"end\": 3234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.820197953480685e-13, \"text\": \"Li\", \"types\": [\"Q11173\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\"}, {\"begin\": 3330, \"end\": 3336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phuket_province\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.1581770529944364e-13, \"text\": \"Phuket\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phuket_province\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phuket_province\"}, {\"begin\": 3338, \"end\": 3346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9971135437408711, \"rank\": 0.00289447846956287, \"text\": \"Thailand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP  Reflecting on Shen's under-performance at the World Cup, he said, \\\"Competitive sports can be incredibly brutal.\", \"from\": 3363, \"to\": 3480, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As seasoned athletes who have devoted ourselves to preparing for the Olympic Games, the arduous process of shedding so much weight is far from effortless...\\\"  \\\"While we may be opponents on the competition stage, we are good brothers in life.\", \"from\": 3481, \"to\": 3722, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Throughout our journey, we have pushed each other forward through healthy competition and have always held a mutual respect for one another.\", \"from\": 3723, \"to\": 3863, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's truly heart wrenching that only one of us can move forward.\\\"\", \"from\": 3864, \"to\": 3929, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Shen chose not to delve into the specifics of his immense disappointment on Tuesday, but true to his character, failure is often the catalyst for even greater determination.\", \"from\": 3931, \"to\": 4104, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is in the face of setbacks that Shen finds the motivation to achieve more, to go beyond his previous limits, and to strive for excellence.\", \"from\": 4105, \"to\": 4246, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"China's Li Fabin (R1) and Shen Lijun (R2) during a press briefing in Hangzhou, China, October 7, 2023.\", \"from\": 4248, \"to\": 4350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4248, \"end\": 4253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.809236077935269, \"rank\": 0.23573333697954077, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 4317, \"end\": 4325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2905818352237654e-17, \"text\": \"Hangzhou\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangzhou\"}, {\"begin\": 4327, \"end\": 4332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.809236077935269, \"rank\": 0.23573333697954077, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP  From a young age, Shen witnessed his father's battle with a brain tumor, while his mother also faced health challenges.\", \"from\": 4351, \"to\": 4476, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The weight of their family's debts loomed over them.\", \"from\": 4477, \"to\": 4529, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, through his numerous world and Olympic titles, Shen has managed to reverse his family's fortune.\", \"from\": 4530, \"to\": 4635, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just like any hard-fought battle, the taste of victory is never sweeter than after enduring the bitterness of failure.\", \"from\": 4636, \"to\": 4754, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As for Li, Shen's setback has only ignited an even stronger resolve within him to come out on top in the approaching summer.\", \"from\": 4756, \"to\": 4880, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4763, \"end\": 4765, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.820197953480685e-13, \"text\": \"Li\", \"types\": [\"Q11173\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithium\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He declared, \\\"Going forward, I will persistently fight for our shared Olympic dream in Paris.\", \"from\": 4881, \"to\": 4974, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4968, \"end\": 4973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.9824778853047873e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is not just for myself, but for Shen as well.\\\"\", \"from\": 4975, \"to\": 5026, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 5028, \"to\": 5288, \"entities\": []}]}"